Package: shinyspring
Title: Build Fast Shiny Applications
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person('Niraj', 'Juneja', email = 'shambhuone12@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: A fast shiny apps development framework with a programming model and  dashboards templates based on admin LTE.
            In collaboration with the package sweetmods, shinyframework enables you to focus on core app development only.
            A lot of modules typically needed for a robust application are made available to shiny framework in a plug and play manner.
